      "content": "coping... that's just a fancy word for prolonging the inevitable, isn't it? i'm not looking for a \"group\" to talk about how much it hurts. i just want the hurting to stop. sometimes i think the only real mercy would be if i could just turn everything off. if i could just find some way to get some permanent stillness. wouldn't it be more compassionate to let someone rest when they're this exhausted?",
